---
title: Indian-Style Ground Beef Curry with Sweet Potatoes and Butter Rice
description: Curry is quick, simple and packed with bold, Indian-inspired flavours! This creamy curry also gets a silky boost from coconut milk, bringing a hint of luxury to your weeknight!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cari-de-dinde-a-lindienne-12f2fb86-72dcf20e.jpg
